	owl:imports <https://w3id.org/nfdi4ing/profiles/ab14d37c-cdf7-4f3d-aa58-b3baa450be15/>, <https://w3id.org/nfdi4ing/profiles/34c941c1-bf9e-425f-9be6-9a2c29c32dae/> ;
